Honda Recalls 693,000 Fit, Freed, City Models Globally

-- B y   M a k i k o   K i t a m u r a
-- 
2011-02-17T06:07:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/honda-recalls-693-000-fit-freed-city-models-correct-.html
Honda Motor Co. will recall about
693,000 Fit, Freed and City models globally to fix motor
problems, spokeswoman Tomoko Uchida said today.  The recalls will take place mostly in  Asia , she said. The
Tokyo-based carmaker is calling back 168,000 units in Japan,
156,000 units in China and 230,000 units in other Asian
countries, Uchida said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Makiko Kitamura in Tokyo at 
 mkitamura1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kae Inoue at 
 kinoue@bloomberg.net  